msg":"推"},{"pid":"e66e6f1519f3d1bad46f21f51036f07a5e4313b8","tid":1360534,"uid":264081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6310340f61aa50b18591fe0135a7aa395b6a1a2","tid":1360534,"uid":237372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲<br />\n5. 全面實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"bcfd0c4260c3d9e318a7f559c98b27e6c696f49d","tid":1360534,"uid":261006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"We connect!!!<br />\n<br />\n- <br />\n不忘721<br />\n不忘5大訴求<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Po9GiPN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPo9GiPN.gif&h=27a04f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>721 [現場] 宣言<br />\n重申對特區政府的 5大訴求:<br />\n<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例修訂，以達至法理上終止修例程序<br />\n2. 收回612暴動定性<br />\n3. 撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n5. 以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「沒有暴民，只有暴政」<br />\n我們誓必以一切可行方式守護香港</strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"50de422576931433015d83d11ef18350d55ca1a9","tid":1360534,"uid":14413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"9d8e252661aa1cc9cb601e25d2cf0d13c84be000","tid":1360534,"uid":48544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee9c76cc007a766003039c17b0437a95487e540","tid":1360534,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply